OL,5, A 78-year-old man has been charged in  
OL,6, connection with the death of a woman   
OL,7, who disappeared nearly 40 years ago.   
OL,9,FMarion Hodge, from Lockerbie, was last 
OL,10,Freported to have been seen in Dumfries 
OL,11,Fin the summer of 1984.                 
OL,13,FShe was declared legally dead by the   
OL,14,FCourt of Session in Edinburgh in 1992  
OL,15,Fand her body has never been found.     
OL,17,FA police statement said that papers had
OL,18,Fnow been served on a man in connection 
OL,19,Fwith her death.                        
